Privacy Policy

We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how Catchinger handles user data and interactions with third-party services. Our game is family-friendly and complies with child privacy laws.

Catchinger does not collect any personal data from its users. However, third-party services such as AdMob and Google Play may collect data for various purposes.

We use third-party services that may collect data:
 - AdMob (for advertising)
 - Google Play (for distribution and analytics) 

For more details, please review their privacy policies:
 - AdMob Privacy Policy
 - Google Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the game and/or on this page.

For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at jakobbrunner.jdm@gmail.com.
